<h2 style="color: #111827; margin-bottom: 20px;">Bestellung erfolgreich aufgegeben!</h2>

<p style="color: #374151; margin-bottom: 15px;">
    Hallo {{firstName}} {{lastName}},
</p>

<p style="color: #374151; margin-bottom: 15px;">
    vielen Dank für Ihre Bestellung! Wir haben Ihre Bestellung erhalten und werden sie schnellstmöglich bearbeiten.
</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3 style="color: #111827; margin-bottom: 15px;">Bestelldetails</h3>

    <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Bestellnummer:</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{orderNo}}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Bestelldatum:</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{orderDate}}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Lieferart:</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{deliveryType}}</span>
    </div>

    {{#if address}}
    <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Lieferadresse:</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{address}}</span>
    </div>
    {{/if}}
</div>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3 style="color: #111827; margin-bottom: 15px;">Artikel</h3>

    {{#each items}}
    <div style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px;">
            <span style="color: #374151; font-weight: 500;">{{this.productName}}</span>
            <span style="color: #6b7280;">{{this.quantity}}x {{this.price}}€</span>
        </div>
        {{#if this.variantName}}
        <div style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">Variante: {{this.variantName}}</div>
        {{/if}}
    </div>
    {{/each}}

    <div style="margin-top: 15px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;">
        <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Zwischensumme:</span>
            <span class="info-value">{{subtotal}}€</span>
        </div>

        {{#if discount}}
        <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Rabatt:</span>
            <span class="info-value" style="color: #059669;">-{{discount}}€</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="info-row">
            <span class="info-label">Liefergebühr:</span>
            <span class="info-value">{{deliveryFee}}€</span>
        </div>

        <div class="info-row" style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 10px;">
            <span class="info-label">Gesamtsumme:</span>
            <span class="info-value" style="color: #111827; font-weight: 700;">{{total}}€</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{{#if paymentType}}
<div style="background-color: #eff6ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p style="color: #1e40af; margin: 0;">
        <strong>Zahlungsart:</strong> {{paymentType}}
    </p>
</div>
{{/if}}

{{#if note}}
<div style="background-color: #fef3c7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p style="color: #92400e; margin: 0;">
        <strong>Ihre Notiz:</strong> {{note}}
    </p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
    Sie erhalten eine weitere E-Mail, sobald sich der Status Ihrer Bestellung ändert.
</p>

<p style="color: #374151; margin-top: 20px;">
    Mit freundlichen Grüßen,<br>
    Ihr {{storeName}} Team
</p>
